In one terminal window run:      
    'perl hstrkr.pl'

And in the same directory, run:  
    'perl hsrdr.pl'

Set the windows aside and then start up hearthstone (in windowed mode) and play. 

The tracker will narrate the game, while the reader will display the following:
    1) Your Drawn Cards
    2) Enemy Cards Played
    3) Enemy Secrets
